Available Tools: get_page_views | get_unique_visitors | get_session_duration | get_bounce_rate
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "url": "string", "from_date": "string", "to_date": "string", "granularity": "hourly|daily|weekly|monthly" }
Response Schema: { "url": "string", "period": "string", "views": number, "unique_visitors": number, "avg_session_seconds": number, "bounce_rate": number }
---
Question: What was the total traffic on the newsletter signup page during the webinar?
Call: { "func_call": "get_page_views", "url": "https://mailchimp.com/signup-webinar", "from_date": "2023-12-05", "to_date": "2023-12-05", "granularity": "hourly" }
Response: { "url": "https://mailchimp.com/signup-webinar", "period": "2023-12-05 to 2023-12-05", "views": 15600, "unique_visitors": 12400, "avg_session_seconds": 340, "bounce_rate": 0.29 }

